### 2. Momentum & Cluster Awareness (The W-Count)

Breadth Draw ($W \ge 4$); Depth Draw ($W \le 3$):

**Trend-Following Rule:**
If the current pattern has repeated for 3+ consecutive weeks, predict the trend to continue. Do not force an oscillation.

**Oscillation Rule:**
If the pattern has repeated for 1–2 weeks, predict a flip (Depth $\rightarrow$ Breadth or vice versa).

