### 4. The Unified Selection Formula (Slot Math)

To ensure no ticket ever contains 7 numbers, all 50 tickets must follow one of these three Mutually Exclusive structures:

| Ticket Type   | Anchor Slots (EH/H) | Body Slots (W) | Wildcard Slot   | Total |
| ------------- | ------------------- | -------------- | --------------- | ----- |
| Pure Strike   | 2                   | 4              | 0               | 6     |
| Legacy Strike | 2                   | 3              | 1 Legacy Number | 6     |
| Cold Strike   | 2                   | 3              | 1 Cold Number   | 6     |

**Anchor Rules:**

* Every ticket must contain exactly 2 Anchors.
* At least one Anchor must come from the H-Pool (or Pseudo-H).
* A ticket may contain maximum one EH number.

