* Legacy Strikes (10 Tickets): 2 Anchors + 3 Body + 1 Legacy. (Focus on "Repeaters").
* Cold Strikes (10 Tickets): 2 Anchors + 3 Body + 1 Cold. (Focus on "Rebounds").

