### 7. The Master Verification Protocol (The Audit)

Perform these three scans on the completed set of 50 before finalization:

**Global Saturation Audit:**
No single number can appear in more than 25% (12.5 tickets) of the total strike. This prevents over-reliance on a single failure point.

**Ratio Balance:**
100% of the set must meet the Odd/Even and High/Low requirements.

**Legacy Sweep:**
Cross-reference every ticket against the previous Saturday's Main 6. Any ticket with $>1$ hit is a Fatal Execution Error.
